datatypes.recordtypes

Class TermekRekord

  • java.lang.Object
    • datatypes.recordtypes.Record
      • datatypes.recordtypes.TermekRekord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TermekRekord
extends Record
implements java.io.Serializable
    The record type for product purchases it also implements the interface serializable and extends the class Record It has all the attributes needed to properly record a product purchase
